detailedDescription.articleBody: Ian M. Desmond is an American professional baseball infielder and outfielder for the Colorado Rockies of Major League Baseball. He previously played for the Washington Nationals and Texas Rangers. Desmond is a three-time Silver Slugger Award winner and a two-time MLB All-Star. While primarily a shortstop throughout his career, Desmond began playing left field and center field for the Rangers in 2016.
